{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I've been in Afghanistan for 21 years."},{"time":2000,"text":"I work for the Red Cross"},{"time":5000,"text":"and I'm a physical therapist."},{"time":9000,"text":"My job is to make arms and legs --"},{"time":12000,"text":"well it's not completely true."},{"time":14000,"text":"We do more than that."},{"time":16000,"text":"We provide the patients,"},{"time":18000,"text":"the Afghan disabled,"},{"time":20000,"text":"first with the physical rehabilitation"},{"time":23000,"text":"then with the social reintegration."},{"time":26000,"text":"It's a very logical plan,"},{"time":29000,"text":"but it was not always like this."},{"time":31000,"text":"For many years, we were just providing them"},{"time":33000,"text":"with artificial limbs."},{"time":36000,"text":"It took quite many years"},{"time":38000,"text":"for the program to become what it is now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"Today, I would like to tell you a story,"},{"time":46000,"text":"the story of a big change,"},{"time":49000,"text":"and the story of the people"},{"time":51000,"text":"who made this change possible."},{"time":53000,"text":"I arrived in Afghanistan"},{"time":55000,"text":"in 1990"},{"time":59000,"text":"to work in a hospital"},{"time":62000,"text":"for war victims."},{"time":64000,"text":"And then, not only for war victims,"},{"time":66000,"text":"but it was for any kind of patient."},{"time":69000,"text":"I was also working"},{"time":71000,"text":"in the orthopedic center, we call it."},{"time":73000,"text":"This is the place where we make the legs."},{"time":76000,"text":"At that time"},{"time":78000,"text":"I found myself"},{"time":80000,"text":"in a strange situation."},{"time":82000,"text":"I felt not quite ready"},{"time":84000,"text":"for that job."},{"time":86000,"text":"There was so much to learn."},{"time":89000,"text":"There were so many things new to me."},{"time":91000,"text":"But it was a terrific job."},{"time":93000,"text":"But as soon as the fighting intensified,"},{"time":95000,"text":"the physical rehabilitation was suspended."},{"time":98000,"text":"There were many other things to do."},{"time":100000,"text":"So the orthopedic center was closed"},{"time":103000,"text":"because physical rehabilitation"},{"time":105000,"text":"was not considered a priority."},{"time":113000,"text":"It was a strange sensation."},{"time":116000,"text":"Anyway, you know every time I make this speech --"},{"time":119000,"text":"it's not the first time -- but it's an emotion."},{"time":122000,"text":"It's something that comes out from the past."},{"time":124000,"text":"It's 21 years,"},{"time":126000,"text":"but they are still all there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"Anyway, in 1992,"},{"time":132000,"text":"the Mujahideen took all Afghanistan."},{"time":135000,"text":"And the orthopedic center was closed."},{"time":138000,"text":"I was assigned to work for the homeless,"},{"time":141000,"text":"for the internally displaced people."},{"time":146000,"text":"But one day, something happened."},{"time":150000,"text":"I was coming back"},{"time":152000,"text":"from a big food distribution in a mosque"},{"time":155000,"text":"where tens and tens of people"},{"time":159000,"text":"were squatting in terrible conditions."},{"time":163000,"text":"I wanted to go home. I was driving."},{"time":166000,"text":"You know, when you want to forget,"},{"time":168000,"text":"you don't want to see things,"},{"time":170000,"text":"so you just want to go to your room, to lock yourself inside"},{"time":173000,"text":"and say, \"That's enough.\""},{"time":177000,"text":"A bomb fell not far from my car --"},{"time":180000,"text":"well, far enough, but big noise."},{"time":183000,"text":"And everybody disappeared from the street."},{"time":187000,"text":"The cars disappeared as well."},{"time":190000,"text":"I ducked."},{"time":192000,"text":"And only one figure"},{"time":194000,"text":"remained in the middle of the road."},{"time":196000,"text":"It was a man in a wheelchair"},{"time":199000,"text":"desperately trying to move away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"Well I'm not a particularly brave person,"},{"time":204000,"text":"I have to confess it,"},{"time":206000,"text":"but I could not just ignore him."},{"time":210000,"text":"So I stopped the car"},{"time":213000,"text":"and I went to help."},{"time":216000,"text":"The man was without legs"},{"time":219000,"text":"and only with one arm."},{"time":222000,"text":"Behind him there was a child, his son,"},{"time":225000,"text":"red in the face"},{"time":227000,"text":"in an effort to push the father."},{"time":231000,"text":"So I took him into a safe place."},{"time":234000,"text":"And I ask, \"What are you doing out in the street"},{"time":238000,"text":"in this situation?\""},{"time":240000,"text":"\"I work,\" he said."},{"time":242000,"text":"I wondered, what work?"},{"time":245000,"text":"And then I ask an even more stupid question:"},{"time":248000,"text":"\"Why don't you have the prostheses?"},{"time":250000,"text":"Why don't you have the artificial legs?\""},{"time":252000,"text":"And he said, \"The Red Cross has closed.\""},{"time":256000,"text":"Well without thinking, I told him"},{"time":259000,"text":"\"Come tomorrow."},{"time":261000,"text":"We will provide you with a pair of legs.\""},{"time":265000,"text":"The man, his name was Mahmoud,"},{"time":268000,"text":"and the child, whose name was Rafi, left."},{"time":272000,"text":"And then I said, \"Oh, my God. What did I say?"},{"time":276000,"text":"The center is closed,"},{"time":278000,"text":"no staff around."},{"time":280000,"text":"Maybe the machinery is broken."},{"time":283000,"text":"Who is going to make the legs for him?\""},{"time":286000,"text":"So I hoped that he would not come."},{"time":290000,"text":"This is the streets of Kabul"},{"time":293000,"text":"in those days."},{"time":296000,"text":"So I said, \"Well I will give him some money.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"And so the following day,"},{"time":301000,"text":"I went to the orthopedic center."},{"time":304000,"text":"And I spoke with a gatekeeper."},{"time":308000,"text":"I was ready to tell him,"},{"time":310000,"text":"\"Listen, if someone such-and-such comes tomorrow,"},{"time":313000,"text":"please tell him that it was a mistake."},{"time":316000,"text":"Nothing can be done."},{"time":318000,"text":"Give him some money.\""},{"time":320000,"text":"But Mahmoud and his son were already there."},{"time":322000,"text":"And they were not alone."},{"time":324000,"text":"There were 15, maybe 20, people like him waiting."},{"time":329000,"text":"And there was some staff too."},{"time":333000,"text":"Among them there was my right-hand man,"},{"time":336000,"text":"Najmuddin."},{"time":338000,"text":"And the gatekeeper told me,"},{"time":341000,"text":"\"They come everyday to see if the center will open.\""},{"time":345000,"text":"I said, \"No."},{"time":347000,"text":"We have to go away. We cannot stay here.\""},{"time":349000,"text":"They were bombing -- not very close -- but you could hear the noise of the bombs."},{"time":352000,"text":"So, \"We cannot stay here, it's dangerous."},{"time":355000,"text":"It's not a priority.\""},{"time":357000,"text":"But Najmuddin told me, \"Listen now, we're here.\""},{"time":361000,"text":"At least we can start repairing the prostheses, the broken prostheses of the people"},{"time":364000,"text":"and maybe try to do something"},{"time":366000,"text":"for people like Mahmoud.\""},{"time":368000,"text":"I said, \"No, please. We cannot do that."},{"time":371000,"text":"It's really dangerous."},{"time":374000,"text":"We have other things to do.\""},{"time":376000,"text":"But they insisted."},{"time":378000,"text":"When you have 20 people"},{"time":380000,"text":"in front of you, looking at you"},{"time":382000,"text":"and you are the one who has to decide ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"So we started doing some repairs."},{"time":388000,"text":"Also one of the physical therapists"},{"time":390000,"text":"reported that Mahmoud"},{"time":392000,"text":"could be provided with a leg,"},{"time":394000,"text":"but not immediately."},{"time":396000,"text":"The legs were swollen"},{"time":398000,"text":"and the knees were stiff,"},{"time":400000,"text":"so he needed a long preparation."},{"time":402000,"text":"Believe me, I was worried"},{"time":404000,"text":"because I was breaking the rules."},{"time":406000,"text":"I was doing something"},{"time":408000,"text":"that I was not supposed to do."},{"time":411000,"text":"In the evening,"},{"time":413000,"text":"I went to speak with the bosses at the headquarters,"},{"time":415000,"text":"and I told them -- I lied --"},{"time":417000,"text":"I told them, \"Listen, we are going to start"},{"time":420000,"text":"a couple of hours per day,"},{"time":423000,"text":"just a few repairs.\""},{"time":425000,"text":"Maybe some of them are here now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"So we started."},{"time":433000,"text":"I was working, I was going everyday"},{"time":436000,"text":"to work for the homeless."},{"time":439000,"text":"And Najmuddin was staying there,"},{"time":441000,"text":"doing everything and reporting on the patients."},{"time":443000,"text":"He was telling me, \"Patients are coming.\""},{"time":446000,"text":"We knew that many more patients"},{"time":448000,"text":"could not come, prevented by the fighting."},{"time":451000,"text":"But people were coming."},{"time":453000,"text":"And Mahmoud was coming every day."},{"time":456000,"text":"And slowly, slowly"},{"time":458000,"text":"week after week"},{"time":460000,"text":"his legs were improving."},{"time":463000,"text":"The stump or cast prosthesis was made,"},{"time":467000,"text":"and he was starting"},{"time":469000,"text":"the real physical rehabilitation."},{"time":472000,"text":"He was coming every day,"},{"time":474000,"text":"crossing the front line."},{"time":476000,"text":"A couple of times I crossed the front line"},{"time":478000,"text":"in the very place where Mahmoud and his son were crossing."},{"time":481000,"text":"I tell you, it was something so sinister"},{"time":484000,"text":"that I was astonished he could do it every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489000,"text":"But finally, the great day arrived."},{"time":493000,"text":"Mahmoud was going to be discharged"},{"time":495000,"text":"with his new legs."},{"time":497000,"text":"It was April, I remember,"},{"time":499000,"text":"a very beautiful day."},{"time":501000,"text":"April in Kabul is beautiful,"},{"time":503000,"text":"full of roses, full of flowers."},{"time":506000,"text":"We could not possibly stay indoors,"},{"time":509000,"text":"with all these sandbags at the windows."},{"time":512000,"text":"Very sad, dark."},{"time":515000,"text":"So we chose a small spot in the garden."},{"time":518000,"text":"And Mahmoud put on his prostheses,"},{"time":521000,"text":"the other patients did the same,"},{"time":524000,"text":"and they started practicing"},{"time":526000,"text":"for the last time before being discharged."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"Suddenly, they started fighting."},{"time":530000,"text":"Two groups of Mujahideen started fighting."},{"time":534000,"text":"We could hear in the air"},{"time":537000,"text":"the bullets passing."},{"time":539000,"text":"So we dashed, all of us,"},{"time":541000,"text":"towards the shelter."},{"time":545000,"text":"Mahmoud grabbed his son, I grabbed someone else."},{"time":547000,"text":"Everybody was grabbing something."},{"time":549000,"text":"And we ran."},{"time":551000,"text":"You know, 50 meters can be a long distance"},{"time":553000,"text":"if you are totally exposed,"},{"time":555000,"text":"but we managed to reach the shelter."},{"time":559000,"text":"Inside, all of us panting,"},{"time":562000,"text":"I sat a moment and I heard Rafi telling his father,"},{"time":566000,"text":"\"Father, you can run faster than me.\""},{"time":569000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":571000,"text":"And Mahmoud, \"Of course I can."},{"time":574000,"text":"I can run, and now you can go to school."},{"time":577000,"text":"No need of staying with me all the day"},{"time":580000,"text":"pushing my wheelchair.\""},{"time":582000,"text":"Later on, we took them home."},{"time":584000,"text":"And I will never forget"},{"time":586000,"text":"Mahmoud and his son walking together"},{"time":589000,"text":"pushing the empty wheelchair."},{"time":592000,"text":"And then I understood,"},{"time":595000,"text":"physical rehabilitation is a priority."},{"time":599000,"text":"Dignity cannot wait for better times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"From that day on, we never closed a single day."},{"time":609000,"text":"Well sometimes we were suspended for a few hours,"},{"time":611000,"text":"but we never, we never closed it again."},{"time":616000,"text":"I met Mahmoud one year later."},{"time":618000,"text":"He was in good shape --"},{"time":622000,"text":"a bit thinner."},{"time":625000,"text":"He needed to change his prostheses --"},{"time":628000,"text":"a new pair of prostheses."},{"time":631000,"text":"I asked about his son."},{"time":633000,"text":"He told me, \"He's at school. He'd doing quite well.\""},{"time":635000,"text":"But I understood he wanted to tell me something."},{"time":639000,"text":"So I asked him, \"What is that?\""},{"time":643000,"text":"He was sweating."},{"time":645000,"text":"He was clearly embarrassed."},{"time":649000,"text":"And he was standing in front of me,"},{"time":652000,"text":"his head down."},{"time":655000,"text":"He said, \"You have taught me to walk."},{"time":659000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":662000,"text":"Now help me not to be a beggar anymore.\""},{"time":666000,"text":"That was the job."},{"time":668000,"text":"\"My children are growing."},{"time":671000,"text":"I feel ashamed."},{"time":673000,"text":"I don't want them to be teased at school"},{"time":676000,"text":"by the other students.\""},{"time":679000,"text":"I said, \"Okay.\""},{"time":681000,"text":"I thought, how much money do I have in my pocket?"},{"time":683000,"text":"Just to give him some money."},{"time":685000,"text":"It was the easiest way."},{"time":687000,"text":"He read my mind,"},{"time":689000,"text":"and he said, \"I ask for a job.\""},{"time":695000,"text":"And then he added something"},{"time":698000,"text":"I will never forget for the rest of my life."},{"time":702000,"text":"He said, \"I am a scrap of a man,"},{"time":708000,"text":"but if you help me,"},{"time":710000,"text":"I'm ready to do anything,"},{"time":713000,"text":"even if I have to crawl on the ground.\""},{"time":717000,"text":"And then he sat down."},{"time":719000,"text":"I sat down too with goosebumps everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727000,"text":"Legless, with only one arm,"},{"time":731000,"text":"illiterate,"},{"time":734000,"text":"unskilled --"},{"time":737000,"text":"what job for him?"},{"time":742000,"text":"Najmuddin told me, \"Well we have a vacancy"},{"time":745000,"text":"in the carpentry shop.\""},{"time":747000,"text":"\"What?\" I said, \"Stop.\""},{"time":752000,"text":"\"Well yes, we need to increase the production of feet."},{"time":757000,"text":"We need to employ someone"},{"time":760000,"text":"to glue and to screw the sole of the feet."},{"time":764000,"text":"We need to increase the production.\""},{"time":767000,"text":"\"Excuse me?\""},{"time":769000,"text":"I could not believe."},{"time":773000,"text":"And then he said,"},{"time":776000,"text":"\"No, we can modify the workbench"},{"time":779000,"text":"maybe to put a special stool,"},{"time":781000,"text":"a special anvil, special vice,"},{"time":785000,"text":"and maybe an electric screwdriver.\""},{"time":787000,"text":"I said, \"Listen, it's insane."},{"time":790000,"text":"And it's even cruel to think of anything like this."},{"time":793000,"text":"That's a production line and a very fast one."},{"time":796000,"text":"It's cruel"},{"time":798000,"text":"to offer him a job"},{"time":800000,"text":"knowing that he's going to fail.\""},{"time":805000,"text":"But with Najmuddin, we cannot discuss."},{"time":809000,"text":"So the only things I could manage to obtain"},{"time":815000,"text":"was a kind of a compromise."},{"time":819000,"text":"Only one week --"},{"time":821000,"text":"one week try and not a single day more."},{"time":824000,"text":"One week later,"},{"time":826000,"text":"Mahmoud was the fastest in the production line."},{"time":830000,"text":"I told Najmuddin, \"That's a trick."},{"time":833000,"text":"I can't believe it.\""},{"time":835000,"text":"The production was up 20 percent."},{"time":837000,"text":"\"It's a trick, it's a trick,\" I said."},{"time":840000,"text":"And then I asked for verification."},{"time":842000,"text":"It was true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"The comment of Najmuddin was Mahmoud has something to prove."},{"time":848000,"text":"I understood"},{"time":850000,"text":"that I was wrong again."},{"time":853000,"text":"Mahmoud had looked taller."},{"time":855000,"text":"I remember him sitting behind the workbench smiling."},{"time":861000,"text":"He was a new man,"},{"time":864000,"text":"taller again."},{"time":867000,"text":"Of course, I understood"},{"time":869000,"text":"that what made him stand tall --"},{"time":873000,"text":"yeah they were the legs, thank you very much --"},{"time":875000,"text":"but as a first step,"},{"time":878000,"text":"it was the dignity."},{"time":880000,"text":"He has regained his full dignity"},{"time":883000,"text":"thanks to that job."},{"time":885000,"text":"So of course, I understood."},{"time":887000,"text":"And then we started a new policy --"},{"time":890000,"text":"a new policy completely different."},{"time":892000,"text":"We decided to employ"},{"time":894000,"text":"as many disabled as possible"},{"time":896000,"text":"to train them in any possible job."},{"time":898000,"text":"It became a policy of \"positive discrimination,\""},{"time":901000,"text":"we call it now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":904000,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":906000,"text":"It's good for everybody."},{"time":908000,"text":"Everybody benefits from that --"},{"time":911000,"text":"those employed, of course,"},{"time":913000,"text":"because they get a job"},{"time":915000,"text":"and dignity."},{"time":917000,"text":"But also for the newcomers."},{"time":919000,"text":"They are 7,000 every year --"},{"time":922000,"text":"people coming for the first time."},{"time":924000,"text":"And you should see the faces of these people"},{"time":926000,"text":"when they realize that those assisting them are like them."},{"time":929000,"text":"Sometimes you see them,"},{"time":931000,"text":"they look, \"Oh.\""},{"time":934000,"text":"And you see the faces."},{"time":936000,"text":"And then the surprise turns into hope."},{"time":943000,"text":"And it's easy for me as well to train someone"},{"time":946000,"text":"who has already passed through the experience of disability."},{"time":949000,"text":"Poof, they learn much faster -- the motivation,"},{"time":953000,"text":"the empathy they can establish with the patient"},{"time":955000,"text":"is completely different, completely."},{"time":959000,"text":"Scraps of men do not exist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":962000,"text":"People like Mahmoud"},{"time":964000,"text":"are agents of change."},{"time":967000,"text":"And when you start changing, you cannot stop."},{"time":970000,"text":"So employing people, yes,"},{"time":972000,"text":"but also we started programming projects"},{"time":975000,"text":"of microfinance, education."},{"time":977000,"text":"And when you start, you cannot stop."},{"time":979000,"text":"So you do vocational training,"},{"time":981000,"text":"home education for those who cannot go to school."},{"time":984000,"text":"Physical therapies can be done, not only in the orthopedic center,"},{"time":986000,"text":"but also in the houses of the people."},{"time":988000,"text":"There is always a better way to do things."},{"time":992000,"text":"That's Najmuddin, the one with the white coat."},{"time":995000,"text":"Terrible Najmuddin, is that one."},{"time":998000,"text":"I have learned a lot"},{"time":1000000,"text":"from people like Najmuddin, Mahmoud, Rafi."},{"time":1002000,"text":"They are my teachers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1004000,"text":"I have a wish, a big wish,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"that this way of working, this way of thinking,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"is going to be implemented in other countries."},{"time":1013000,"text":"There are plenty of countries at war like Afghanistan."},{"time":1018000,"text":"It is possible and it is not difficult."},{"time":1021000,"text":"All we have to do"},{"time":1023000,"text":"is to listen to the people"},{"time":1026000,"text":"that we are supposed assist,"},{"time":1029000,"text":"to make them part"},{"time":1031000,"text":"of the decision-making process"},{"time":1034000,"text":"and then, of course, to adapt."},{"time":1037000,"text":"This is my big wish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1041000,"text":"Well don't think that the changes in Afghanistan are over;"},{"time":1044000,"text":"not at all. We are going on."},{"time":1046000,"text":"Recently we have just started a program,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"a sport program --"},{"time":1051000,"text":"basketball for wheelchair users."},{"time":1053000,"text":"We transport the wheelchairs everywhere."},{"time":1056000,"text":"We have several teams in the main part of Afghanistan."},{"time":1059000,"text":"At the beginning,"},{"time":1061000,"text":"when Anajulina told me,"},{"time":1064000,"text":"\"We would like to start it,\""},{"time":1066000,"text":"I hesitated."},{"time":1068000,"text":"I said, \"No,\" you can imagine."},{"time":1070000,"text":"I said, \"No, no, no, no, we can't.\""},{"time":1072000,"text":"And then I asked the usual question:"},{"time":1074000,"text":"\"Is it a priority?"},{"time":1076000,"text":"Is it really necessary?\""},{"time":1079000,"text":"Well now you should see me."},{"time":1081000,"text":"I never miss a single training session."},{"time":1084000,"text":"The night before a match I'm very nervous."},{"time":1087000,"text":"And you should see me during the match."},{"time":1091000,"text":"I shout like a true Italian."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1094000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1097000,"text":"What's next? What is going to be the next change?"},{"time":1101000,"text":"Well I don't know yet,"},{"time":1103000,"text":"but I'm sure Najmuddin and his friends,"},{"time":1105000,"text":"they have it already in mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1107000,"text":"That was my story. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1110000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}